## Commands

When building storefront pages, follow these workflows:
- **generate-landing-page**: Generate a complete Shopify landing page from a brief or ad creative (uses: storefront-craft, workflow-orchestration, conversion-psychology, page-generation)
- **optimize-page**: Analyze and optimize an existing landing page for better conversions (uses: conversion-psychology, page-editing, analytics)
